name: __EQuarztQuantizationReference
doc:
An enumeration for specifying quantization boundary reference frame
display name to hide c++ typo for now

BarRelative: Will occur on the next occurence of this duration from the start of a bar (i.e. On beat 3)
TransportRelative: Will occur on the next multiple of this duration since the clock started ticking (i.e. on the next 4 bar boundary)
CurrentTimeRelative: Will occur on the next multiple of this duration from the current time (i.e. In three beats)
